# Nesting
- SCSS rules should ideally nest to match hierarchical usage in the component tree. e.g.:
	```tsx
	// ImageGallery.tsx
	return <div className={styles.gallery}>
			<figure className={styles.imageWrapper}>
				<img className={styles.image}/>
				<figcaption className={styles.caption}>
					Hello world.
				</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>
	);
	```

	```scss
	// ImageGallery.module.scss
	.gallery {
		// ...
		.imageWrapper {
			// ...
			.image {
				// ...
			}

			.caption {
				// ...
			}
		}
	}
	```